    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🌿 Vaidik Greens — Social Media Image Publisher\n\n**Workflow Flow:**\n1. Upload image via form (title & description are optional)\n2. Image is **resized & converted to WebP** (under 150 KB) using Edit Image node\n3. **OpenAI GPT-4o** analyzes the image and generates:\n   - SEO-friendly title\n   - Engaging caption with emojis\n   - Relevant hashtags\n   - Alt text for accessibility\n4. Image is uploaded to **WordPress** media library\n5. Post is published to **Facebook**, **Instagram**, and **Google My Business**\n\n---\n\n### ⚙️ Setup Required\n\n**1. Edit the \"Set Config\" node** with your actual:\n- WordPress URL (already set to vaidikgreens.com)\n- Facebook Page ID\n- Instagram Business User ID\n- Google My Business Account & Location IDs\n\n**2. Create Credentials in n8n:**\n- **OpenAI API** — Add your OpenAI API key\n- **WordPress Basic Auth** — Username + Application Password\n- **Facebook Page Token** (HTTP Header Auth) — `Authorization: Bearer TOKEN`\n- **Google OAuth2** — Client ID + Secret\n\n**3. Instagram** uses the same Facebook/Meta token.\n\n**4. No environment variables needed!** ✅\nThis version uses built-in n8n nodes (no sharp dependency).\n\n### 🔗 Reference URLs (for finding IDs)\n\n**Facebook Page:** https://www.facebook.com/vaidikgreensresort\n**Instagram:** https://www.instagram.com/vaidikgreensresort2025/\n**Google Reviews:** https://www.google.com/travel/hotels/entity/CgoI1evv1KKZidh1EAE/reviews",
        "height": 640,
        "width": 530,
        "color": 4
      },
